item.title: V00070
item.description: Very rare Ford Mailam 5001L-6 agricultural crawler tractor, 6 cylinder engine, 112HP, (Ford 5000 super six engine and transmission) ex farm condition, original paint, auxiliary hydraulics, drawbar, very good undercarriage, only very few of this type of tractor was produced. Collectors item! Inspection are welcome. Road/Sea transport can be arranged!
